    <item>
      <title>爱立信价值下跌，一年内第二次对 Vonage 进行减记</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ericsson-takes-second-vonage-writedown-in-a-year-as-value-sinks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱立信公司警告投资者，由于 Vonage Holdings Corp. 的业绩恶化，该公司将在第二季度计提 114 亿瑞典克朗（11 亿美元）的非现金减值，这是不到一年内该资产第二次大幅减值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ericsson-takes-second-vonage-writedown-in-a-year-as-value-sinks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:05:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
